Let $M$ be a matroid with ground set $W$, and suppose $k$ is a positive integer. Then a subset $S\subseteq W$ is:

\begin{itemize}

\item a \emph{cyclic} $k$\emph{-separation} of $M$ if $\lambda(S)<k$ and both
