\begin{itemize}
\item[{\rm (A1)}]\Label{ass-arc} Each \cpl\ meets $\C$ in a $q$-arc.  
\item[{\rm (A2)}] \Label{ass-uniq} Any two distinct \cpt s lie in a unique \cpl.
